ClubLeader "1" --> "0..*" Club : manages
Club "1" *-- "0..*" Event : owns
Club "1" *-- "0..*" Announcement : posts
Club "1" o-- "0..*" ClubMembership : has
Student "1" --> "0..*" ClubMembership : requests
Student "1" --> "0..*" EventRegistration : makes
Event "1" --> "0..*" EventRegistration : receives
Administrator "1" --> "0..*" FlaggedContent : reviews

Event --> EventState : currentState
EventState <|.. DraftEventState
